membership:
MIJARC Europe is member of MIJARC World, the European Youth Forum and the European Coordination La Via Campesina.&#xd;
It is also partner of Rural Youth Europe and FIMARC.&#xd;
MIJARC Europe is represented on the Advisory Council on Youth of the European Youth Foundation (Council of Europe).

